**Non-tile based games**, which can be called ‚Äúpolygon based games‚Äù are more complex.  
In such game, like a *Worms* or a *Sonic*, it‚Äôs totally crazy to write the map by hand (objects positions, polygons coordinates, ‚Ä¶). The alternative, is not to use predefined maps, but on-the-fly generated maps which doesn‚Äôt fit every games.

